OL,8,     GPowys. But the decor disappoints
OL,9,     Gone guest, and there's a frosty
OL,10,     Gatmosphere at breakfast.
OL,11,G2025FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GIt's the final day of the
OL,13,     Gcompetition and the B&Bers meet
OL,14,     Gfor the last time. Things get
OL,15,     Gpersonal and there are dramatic
OL,16,     Gdiscoveries before the payments
OL,17,     Gare made and the winner is
OL,18,     Gannounced.
